作者：
zewen.wu To change this generated comment edit the template variable "typecomment": Window>Preferences>Java>Templates. To enable and disable the creation of type comments go to Window>Preferences>Java>Code Generation. This class is a custom action intended to be used in the body of an EncodeURLTag or a RedirectTag. It adds the specified parameter name and value to it's parent's list of parameters. It can be used in the body of any tag handler that implements the ParamParent interface., Hans Bergsten, Gefion software
